                "institute": "2SWDUPP"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " For proton energies in the range",
                " 6 to 11 MeV the accelerator at Uppsala (TLU), Sweden"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDGT"
                ],
                "institute": "2DENNBI"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " For proton energies in the range 10 to",
                "17 MeV the accelerator at the Niels Bohr Institute"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDGT"
                ],
                "institute": "1CANCRC"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " For proton energies in the range 12.5",
                "to 24 MeV were performed at Chalk River Nuclear",
                "Laboratories (CRNL), Chalk River, Canada."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets were prepared from two batches of",
                "isotopically separated ytterbium.",
                " * One batch contained 96.43% 176Yb. The targets were",
                "   self-supporting with thicknesses ranging from",
                "   1.4 to 8.6 mg/cm2.",
                " * Another batch was enriched to 99.62% 176Yb and",
                "   deposited on 1.5 mg/cm2 thick aluminium backings.",
                "   The amount of ytterbium in the targets ranged",
                "   from 0.2 to 0.5 mg/cm2. All foils were mounted in",
                "   aluminium frames with 8 mm circular holes."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The activity was measured with high-resolution",
                "germanium detectors. At CRNL a planar detector with a",
                "resolution of 1.9 keV (FWHM) at 200 keV was used."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " coaxial Ge(Li) detector with the same resolution",
                "in two other Laboratories."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The gamma-ray detector was a NaI(T1) crystal,",
                "22.6 cm in diameter and 20.8 cm long, placed at",
                "90.degr. with respect to the ion beam at a distance of",
                "about 1 m from the target. The detector was shielded",
                "with lead and borated paraffin."
              ]
            }
          ],
